data.description: This charming ranch home is nestled in the lovely neighborhood of Slater Village. When you walk through the door, you are greeted with modern vinyl flooring and tall, smooth ceilings. Picture yourself hosting a game night with family and friends in the cozy living room. The eat-in kitchen is adorned with gorgeous granite countertops and sleek stainless steel appliances. The spacious master bedroom is flooded with natural light. Step out back and onto the deck, when you can enjoy an early morning cup of coffee, alfresco dining, or your favorite drink after a long day of work. This home is conveniently located near the mountains, great for those who love to explore the outdoors, and schools are all nearby, for those who have school age children. Additionally, this home is just a short 10 minute drive from the serene town of Traveler's Rest, where you can find an abundance of shopping, dining and entertainment options! Don't miss out on this gem! Come see it today!
